        content: 'This Privacy Policy (hereinafter "Policy") outlines how Knowhere Inc. (hereinafter the "Company") collects, uses, and manages Personal Information of users (hereinafter "User(s)") in relation to the "SmartScout" service (hereinafter the "Service"). The Company is committed to protecting Personal Information by complying with all applicable law in the territories where it is offered, including, but not limited to, all applicable United States state and federal law, the Act on the Protection of Personal Information of Japan and other relevant laws and regulations, and by handling Personal Information appropriately.'
