        content: 'The Company will acquire Personal Information by appropriate and lawful means. The Company uses the information collected for a variety of purposes. The Company\'s legal bases for processing a User\'s Personal Information are: 1) the Company\'s legitimate interest in running and maintaining the Service and the Company\'s business; 2) performance and fulfillment of contracts; 3) a User\'s consent; and 4) compliance with legal obligations. In many instances, more than one of these legal bases apply to the processing of a User\'s Personal Information.  The Company may collect the following Personal Information from Users when they use the Service or when such information is provided by Users:\n\nInformation provided by the User: e.g. name, address, telephone number, email address, date of birth, and other profile or contact information that the User enters when registering for or using the Service.  Users may also submit audio, video, and other data related to a User\'s athletic profile, which will be treated Personal Information for the purposes of this Policy and the Terms.\n\nInformation related to Service usage: e.g. usage history of the Service, access logs, device information, cookies and similar identifiers, and any data (including images, videos, or performance metrics) that the User uploads or inputs into the Service, including play videos (such as pitching and batting actions, among others).\n\nLocation information: Device location data obtained when the User permits the use of location services within the Service.\n\nPayment information: Information related to credit card details and other payment methods collected when purchasing paid content or making transactions within the Service, including information obtained through external services such as Apple or Stripe necessary for payment processing.\n\nOther information obtained in connection with the User\'s use of the Service: Any additional Personal Information that the Company needs to collect for operating or improving the Service, which will be obtained by appropriate means and with prior notice to the User when required.'
